turnkey-pde (1.2) testing; urgency=low

  * Initial release (1.0) TurnKey Portable Development Environment
    - LXC and LXD from Ubuntu xenial-backports
    - dnsmasq provides DNS for container domains .lxc and .lxd
    - lxc-turnkey template and inithooks.conf from TurnKey LXC appliance
    - lxd-turnkey downloads lxc v1 image and converts to lxd v2 image

     John Carver <dude4linux@gmail.com>  Tue, 06 Feb 2018 00:00:00 -0500

  * Release (1.1) 
    - bug fixes
    - updated version of lxc-turnkey template
    - apt-cacher-ng apt caching proxy for all containers
    - new lxd-make-image for tkldev appliance

     John Carver <dude4linux@gmail.com>  Sat, 17 Mar 2018 17:58:47 -0500

  * Release (1.2)
    - modularized pde-setup putting files in ./overlay and scripts in ./conf.d
    - updated to support versions 3.x of LXC and LXD now in xenial-backports
    - updated to support TurnKey version 15.0 based on Debian stretch
    - replaced --force option with --update
    - initialize LXD only during first install
    - stop containers before update, restart after

 -- John Carver <dude4linux@gmail.com>  Tue, 17 Jul 2018 16:37:52 +0000
